Termitron/Nightlight/Windlord

Termitron::

Termitron continued attaking a his enemies while he avoided their 
attacks; he shot 5 shots against MacGowan, 5 against Stiller, 10 
against Virgo, and 5 against Alba.

Nightlight::


Nightlight quickly moved backwards while she used her left wing to 
cover herself, Depp's struck made a wound in Nightlight's wings, she 
moved quickly her wing and fired 25 energy balls against Depp. She 
fell fear, she was wondering if she and her friends would survive.
 

Windlord::


Windlord dogged most of the Barrymore's, Lee's shots and he avoided 
McGowan's missile; he fired 5 shots against Barrymore, 5 against Lee 
and 15 against  McGowan
